##*Political Economist seeking opportunities*

I am a recent graduate of the Master's Degree in Comparative Politics at the University of Bergen. My thesis is written in the field of comparative political economy, on the topic of "How the organization of labor unions and politics matter for economic performance".

##Projects
Here you'll find various code-related projects, or pieces of code I've saved for later use.

###[Applications Analysis](http://olevik.me/applications) [(GH Repo)](https://github.com/OleVik/ApplicationsAnalysis)
